productReviews.reviewText: The box this comes in is 3 yard by 6 light-year and weights 11 megaton!!
My velociraptor loves to play with it.
My co-worker Delton has one of these. He says it looks slender.
My co-worker Erick has one of these. He says it looks fluffy.
This Cape works very well. It harmonically improves my tennis by a lot.
